the steering wheel controls do not work
a clicking sound is heard when the steering wheel is turned
and the passenger occupant detection system control module fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the air bag warning light can indicate a problem with the air bag system, which can lead to serious injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The air bag warning light illuminates
the air bag system fails to deploy
and the passenger occupant detection system control module fails.
